snippet.title: Modern Production Fundamentals - Mike Doom for Amber Academy
snippet.description:
This time, Mike Doom, Executive Producer and Game Director, was our guest speaker.

Theme: Modern Production Fundamentals 🎮🎮
You'll get insights on:

1. Understand what it takes to be a Producer of Today
2. How to organize a team for maximum efficiency 
3. How to structure and pace workflow in development and live ops
4. A warchest of proven F2P tactics from Mike's mobile and social playbook
